metadata.title: RNAS, Wilderness Study Areas - CNF

creators.name: USDA Forest Service, Chugach National Forest

metadata.description: Data Type: Boundaries; Special administration polygons with Research Natural Areas by name, Wilderness Study Areas and Recommended Wilderness coded accordingly. Coverage RNACNF contains all the Research Natural Areas proposed for the Chugach National Forest. Coverage WILDERNESS contains the Wilderness Study Area mandated by ANILCA and the Wilderness recommended by the 1984 Plan.
